title: Goosebumps Complete
description: Here is Goosebumps Complete Series edited with out commercials. I took this torrentand went through every episode and edited out the stupid jetex and fox commercials. Also re-compressed them. All episodes are Divx 3 code for video and mp3 code for audio. Season 3 Episode one day at horrorland is taken from 5 parts flv files from youtube. It is the complete episode parts 1 and 2 combined. Part 1 ends with credits then part 2 begins with the beginning credits. Hope everyone enjoys I took alot of time to do this. Also some episodes that are parts 1 and 2 I combined into one file. All epiosdes should be ok with audio and video sync except for season 3 episode Werewolf Skin pt1 where it gets off towards the end. I tried fixing it but then it made it worse so I left it alone.
